  <text>
    <body>
      <div>
        <head>SCENA SETTIMA ED ULTIMA</head>
		<stage><persName xml:id="Fernando"><forename>Fernando</forename></persName> che esce dal coro, e <persName xml:id="Baldassarre"><forename>Baldassarre</forename></persName></stage>
        <sp>
          <speaker><persName corresp="#Fernando"><forename>FERNANDO</forename></persName></speaker>
          <l>
            Ah padre, è <rs type="coreference"><ref target="#Leonora"/>dessa</rs>!
          </l>
          <l>
             Mia <persName xml:id="Leonora"><forename>Leonora</forename></persName>.
          </l>
        </sp>
        <sp>
          <speaker><persName corresp="#Baldassarre"><forename>BALDASSARE</forename></persName></speaker>
          <stage>(si abbassa verso il cadavere e <rs type="coreference"><ref target="#Leonora"/>riconoscendola</rs>)</stage>
          <l>
            Oh, chi vegg'io!
          </l>
        </sp>
        <sp>
          <speaker><persName corresp="#Fernando"><forename>FERNANDO</forename></persName></speaker>
          <l>
            <persName corresp="#Leonora"><forename>Leonora</forename></persName>!
          </l>
        </sp>
        <sp>
          <speaker><persName corresp="#Baldassarre"><forename>BALDASSARE</forename></persName></speaker>
          <l>
            Silenzio, <rs type="coreference"><ref target="#Leonora"/>ella</rs> è già spenta.
          </l>
          <stage>(poi si volge verso gli <rs type="coreference"><ref target="#Tutti"/>altri</rs>)</stage>
          <l>
            Sul peregrin novello, le vostre preci: ei più non vive.
          </l>
        </sp>
        <sp>
          <speaker><persName corresp="#Fernando"><forename>FERNANDO</forename></persName></speaker>
          <l>
            Anch'io avrò diman la vostra prece.
          </l>
        </sp>
        <sp>
          <speaker xml:id="Tutti">TUTTI</speaker>
          <l>
            Oh Dio!
          </l>
        </sp>
      </div>
